"compatibility with other systems, use this method.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>i-des</b>, indlela ehlala ikhona ye-Linux, isebenza kuzo zonke iimo "
"ezingqonge umsebenzi wothungelwano,\n"
"kodwa ikubophelela kumagama okugqithisa angemadanga kwiimpawu ezithatha "
"izithuba ezisibhozo. Ukuba ufuna\n"
" ungqinelwano nezinye izixokelelwano, sebenzisa le ndlela.</p>"

#. Password dialog help 5c/8
#: src/include/security/helps.rb:139
msgid ""
"<p><b>MD5</b> allows longer passwords and is supported by all current "
"Linux \n"
"distributions, but not by other systems or old software.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>i-MD5</b> ivumela amagama okugqithisa amade noko kwaye ixhaswa ngabo "
"bonke abasasazi be-Linux \n"
"bangoku, kodwa ingezizo ezinye izixokelelwano okanye okungaphakathi "
"ekhompyutheni okudala.</p>"

#. Password dialog help 5d/8
#: src/include/security/helps.rb:143
msgid ""
"<p><b>SHA-512</b> is the current standard hash method, using other "
"algorithms is not recommended unless needed for compatibility purpose.</p>"
msgstr ""

#. Password dialog help 7/8
#: src/include/security/helps.rb:147
msgid ""
"<p><b>Password Age:</b> Set the minimum and\n"
"maximum number of days a password may be used.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>Ubudala Begama Lokugqithisa:</b> Misela inani leentsuku elilelona "
"lincinci kunye\n"
"nelilelona lininzi elinokusetyenziswa ngalo igama lokugqithisa.</p>"

#. Password dialog help 8/8
#: src/include/security/helps.rb:151
msgid ""
"<p><b>Days before Password Expires Warning</b>: This entry sets the\n"
"number of days users are warned before their passwords expire. The longer "
"the\n"
"time, the less likely it is that someone can guess passwords.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>Iintsuku phambi Kwesilumkiso Sokudlulelwa Lixesha Legama Lokugqithisa</"
"b>: Eli ngeniso limisela inani leentsuku abasebenzisi abalumkiswa ngalo "
"phambi kokudlulelwa lixesha kwamagama okugqithisa. Ngokobude \n"
"bexesha, kuya ngokuba yinto enqabileyo ukuba umntu aqashisele ngamagama "
"okugqithisa.</p>"

